Spain’s PP Plans to Sell Ads on Public TV, Confidencial Says

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-04-12T06:40:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/spain-s-pp-plans-to-sell-ads-on-public-tv-confidencial-says.html
Spain ’s  People’s Party , the
opposition group that is leading in opinion polls ahead of next
year’s election, plans to return to selling advertising on the
country’s public television stations, El Confidencial website
reported, citing party officials without naming them.   The party is considering seeking sponsorship for programs
rather than filling traditional ad breaks to avoid diverting
revenue from private broadcasters, the website said.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
